{"tid":1623610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好唔記得信德","createTime":"2019-10-05T00:19:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T13:38:50.000Z","uid":119135,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"527a105f50d35be656ce36a6cc7cf9d2d352542e","tid":1623610,"uid":119135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:19:46.000Z","msg":"澳門賭王何鴻燊的女兒何超瓊，以及美心集團創辦人伍沾德的女兒伍淑清兩個身家過億的女商人，將在星期二出席聯合國人權理事會，為港府最近數個月對付示威者的政策辯護。根據南華早報引述兩人的演講詞，現年57歲的何超瓊和71歲的伍淑清批評反對逃犯條例修訂只屬於&ldquo;一小撮示威者的意見，並不能代表750萬香港人&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n而家得美心有裝修 提議參觀信德中心<br />\n主題係唔好賭錢<br />\n<br />\n1. 好多大陸人往來 就算賭都要去美資場<br />\n2. 好多大陸 澳門公司 直撃要害 例如澳門賽馬會<br />\n3. 有美心 元氣 Starbucks 中銀 吉野同場 唔使走太遠<br />\n4. 交通方便 易去又易走"},{"pid":"06c2d73859775fe70e89d4dc105033704383400b","tid":1623610,"uid":301067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:27:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f02cbbbed6b7345d75d80db2115bcdeb671a8046","tid":1623610,"uid":119135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:30:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8bfc80eb51f9724e4aa72eff2cacda111a51ef60","tid":1623610,"uid":119135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:37:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f66e2b40bbdc0525112d164e4ecf4dd2f152886","tid":1623610,"uid":37303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:38:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"223cfd954d85e3438e004bd494797b089cb3c761","tid":1623610,"uid":48703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:38:41.000Z","msg":"隔離就係狗竇喎清<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e15191b8387e3fbc296d3d5657130157bb8272","tid":1623610,"uid":119135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"223cfd954d85e3438e004bd494797b089cb3c761","tid":1623610,"uid":48703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T00:38:41.000Z","msg":"隔離就係狗竇喎清<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.g